title: Colorful Birds on a Branch
description: The image features two vibrant birds perched on a branch. One bird is feeding the other, showcasing a mix of bright colors including turquoise, yellow, and reddish-brown. The background is plain, emphasizing the birds and their interaction.

title: Salt Flats at Sunset
description: A scenic view of salt flats with vibrant red water reflecting the sunset. The landscape features raised pathways made of sand or salt, dividing the shallow pools of water. The horizon shows a distant city skyline, adding depth to the tranquil scene.

title: Coastal Dunes
description: A scenic view of sandy dunes leading down to a calm blue sea, with a mountainous landscape in the background under a clear blue sky.
